OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1783765122
OL,3,CLancashire farmer says heatwaves 'turn
OL,4,Cyour life upside down'
OL,6,FFarmers in the region say they are
OL,7,Fstruggling with the impact of extreme
OL,8,Fweather conditions.
OL,10,FThe latest heatwave - the third this
OL,11,Fyear - is expected to bring
OL,12,Ftemperatures of more than 30 degrees.
OL,14,FFarmer Andrew Webster, from Hollin
OL,15,FHouse Farm, Aughton, West Lancashire,
OL,16,Fhas been growing potatoes since he was
OL,17,Fa boy.
OL,19,FBut he's worried this could be his
OL,20,Fworst ever crop.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,367,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1783765122
OL,3,CLancashire farmer says heatwaves 'turn
OL,4,Cyour life upside down'
OL,6,F"It turns your life upside down when
OL,7,Fit's like this because we're having to
OL,8,Fbe spraying at three or four o'clock
OL,9,Fin the morning before the heat gets
OL,10,Fup," he said.
OL,12,FThe challenge to adapt means spending
OL,13,Fmore money.
OL,15,F"At some point we'll have to build
OL,16,Fsome big reservoirs if we want to
OL,17,Fcarry on irrigating these crops,
OL,18,Flaying all the pipes out, it's a big
OL,19,Fcost, a cost we will have to try to
OL,20,Fabsorb.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,367,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1783765122
OL,3,CLancashire farmer says heatwaves 'turn
OL,4,Cyour life upside down'
OL,6,F"Mother Nature will always win."
OL,8,FSeparately the National Farmers Union
OL,9,Fhas said British farmers are already
OL,10,Ffacing extreme weather events and
OL,11,Fthese are expected to increase in
OL,12,Ffrequency and intensity.
OL,14,FThe NFU said farmers and growers are
OL,15,Ftaking a number of steps to build
OL,16,Fresilience but need government help to
OL,17,Fadapt.
OL,19,FMeanwhile consultant dermatologist
OL,20,FProfessor Faisal Ali said people must
OL,21,Fprotect themselves from the sun.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,367,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1783765122
OL,3,CLancashire farmer says heatwaves 'turn
OL,4,Cyour life upside down'
OL,6,F"The big one we need to worry about is
OL,7,Fskin cancer," he said. "If you have a
OL,8,Fblistering skin burn it can hugely
OL,9,Fincrease your risk of a life
OL,10,Fthreatening skin cancer called
OL,11,Fmelanoma later in life."
OL,13,FProfessor Ali said that on the hottest
OL,14,Fdays people should consider avoiding
OL,15,Fthe sun between 11am and 2pm, wearing
OL,16,Flong-sleeved clothing, wide-brimmed
OL,17,Fhats, and sunglasses.
OL,19,FHe advises checking skin once a month
OL,20,Fand reporting any changes to a GP or
OL,21,Fdermatologist.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,367,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1783765122
OL,3,CLancashire farmer says heatwaves 'turn
OL,4,Cyour life upside down'
OL,6,F"The other important thing is to use a
OL,7,Fregular sunscreen as well and the
OL,8,Flabelling can be confusing. The things
OL,9,Fto watch out for are that it's SPF 30
OL,10,For above and that it has UVA
OL,11,Fprotection," he said.
OL,13,F"Remember the sun as it is at the
OL,14,Fmoment in the UK is more powerful now
OL,15,Fthan in other parts of Europe at this
OL,16,Ftime of year as well so you do need to
OL,17,Ftreat it with the respect it deserves."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
